{
  "stem": "1132.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was down in the basement with my mother, my sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My father wasn't there, because every time he heard that there be another roundup coming, he left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know how he did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I really don't know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as he walked out, the story went-- and this is his story-- that he was watching as the Nazis were collecting group of people to see whether we were there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a zigzag.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He went into the building that they left, and he ran from the building that they were going to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I absolutely don't know how he did it, but he did it, because he survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was doing this in that famous quote that my mother took to him, with the yellow Star of David on him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have two yellow stars here to show you, and one of them is very dirty and dark.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my father's, because he's the one who was always out and always wearing it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's really an amazing situation how he survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, at one of these roundups, they wanted to take my sister, who was an able-bodied young teenager.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she came up with a story that nobody has ever rehearsed or told her to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the story was the following-- I can't walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What good would I do for you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they said, what do you mean you can't walk?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they marched her up and down in the basement, and she was limping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was sort of having one foot being limp and just saying, I can't walk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now why was she saying that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because earlier, about six months or so, she broke her leg, and she was in a cast.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
